<strong><font color="crimson">JF:</font> </strong>Kind of adorable, really, although the girl&#8217;s face could be more prominent.</p>
<hr />
<p><font color="darkred">Diane Escalera</font> submitted <strong>Latin Heat Trilogy</strong> designed by Gilded Heart Design. &#8220;Latin Heat Trilogy features all three stories in the collection together for the first time in one sizzling edition.&#8221;<br />
