designed by Jennifer Quinlan. &#8220;&#8221;Corral Nocturne&#8221; is a short Western retelling of the Cinderella story. I was delighted with the way Jenny Quinlan brought to life my idea for something that would fit the setting and yet have a bit of a fairytale flavor too (the tumbledown fence references the title and a key scene in the story).&#8221;<br />
