<p><font color="darkred">Elizabeth McCoy</font> submitted <strong>Crucible</strong> designed by Elizabeth McCoy; art by Sarah Cloutier. &#8220;I&#8217;m not entirely happy with the title&#8217;s size; my spouse insisted there should be more space at the edges, while I pointed out hardcovers with narrower title margins. Author-name font is for the fantasy-romance series; title font for this book&#8217;s low romance content (like a prior same-world short).&#8221;<br />
